Package: hercpanorama
Title: Wrangle data from the Panorama Student Information System
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Ben", "Taft", , "ben.taft@career2cradle.org", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Higher Expectations for Racine County", role = "cph")
  )
Description:
    Student-level data from Panoram is export as wide-formatted csv files. Each
    file has common identifying and demographic data, then many, possibly
    unique, columns corresponding to scores on assessments or responses to
    surveys. The names of these columns include information about the type of
    data collected as well as when the data were collected. There are also
    usually two columns for every assessment, a raw score and a grade.
